Simple play application bootstrapped from the activator.

This is not a show case application, it is a mechanism for learning the play framework.

Post data:

<pre>
curl -v -X POST localhost:9000/computers --data '{"name":"lappy","manufacturer":"acme"}' -H 'content-type:application/json'
</pre>


To pick up new dependencies via sbt when connected to the internet via a proxy, use the http_proxy and https_proxy
environment variables.